Long:

                         GiGA Productions presents
 

 	Name: Global Hazard - An Amostration demo by GiGA Productions.
 	
 	Note: It's over a year old. It's our third. 
           It's made 100% in AmosPro + Craft extension.
           This is our last Amos demo, though we are still using Amos for other
	      things. Our comming amiga/pc/java demos will be pure C/C++/Java/Asm. 
 	
 	History:

	v1.0 - Released at 'The South Sealand Demo Party 1996' (SSP'96) in Denmark.
	       Ranked: among the bottom, caused by the machine they runned the demos
	               on, A1230 with FPU!!! The only Amiga it doesn't work with! AFAIK.

Missing sourcecode:
