Known (remembered) bugs: 
	
 040 and probably 060 users: Boot without startup, no setpatch, start demo.
	
 If the demo crashes etc.., then try the 040/060 startup method, or get more mem!
	
 It has a bad habit of crashing sometimes...  but it's very seldom. don't worry!
	
 I haven't been able to run it on A1230 with FPU. 020 and 040 work okay though. (?)
                 
                      Only Amiga makes it possible!!!
